text: La Lisa () is one of the 15 municipalities or boroughs (municipios in Spanish) in the city of Havana, Cuba. ==Overview== It has 7 neighbourhoods: *Alturas de La Lisa *Arroyo Arenas *Balcón Arimao *El Cano-Valle Grande-Bello 26 y Morado *Punta Brava *San Agustín *Versalles-Coronela. It can be generally thought of as a semi-rural municipality. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Municipalities of Havana
title: La Lisa
